```yml
created_at: [YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS]
type: refactor
component: [Nombre componente refactorizado]
Razón: [Descripción breve por qué]
author: [Nombre]
Alcance: [Número de archivos/líneas afectadas]
tests_passing: [SI/NO]
Performance impact: [Ninguno/Mejora/Degradación]
Estimado esfuerzo: [horas]
```

refactor(scope): short description of refactoring

Explain the reason for refactoring:
- Code smell that was addressed
- Performance issue solved
- Maintainability improvement
- Structure clarification

Explain the refactoring:
- How the code was reorganized
- What changed structurally (not functionally)
- Patterns or principles applied
- Migration path if complex

Impact:
- Files affected: [list]
- Lines changed: [roughly]
- Breaking changes: [none/list them]
- Performance impact: [neutral/improved/slightly slower]
- Backward compatibility: [fully/partially/broken]

Behavior:
- Functional behavior: [unchanged/improved]
- Tests before: [passing/failing]
- Tests after: [passing/failing]

Examples:
refactor(database): consolidate user queries into repository pattern
refactor(api): extract common validation into middleware
refactor(structure): reorganize project directories per conventions
refactor(code): remove code duplication in auth service
